  "text": "Fat and lean mass were evaluated by quantitative magnetic resonance imaging (QMR) with the EchoMRI-3-in-1 system (Echo Medical System, Houston, TX, USA), as described [CITATION_1] . The procedure requires immobilizing the mice in plastic restrainer tubes without sedation and takes <2 min per mouse.",
